          "name": "Frightful",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "A creature who is within 100 feet of a siege dragon at the start of its turn must succeed a Will save (DC 39) or become frightened 2. Regardless of the result of the saving throw, the creature is then temporarily immune to this effect for 24 hours.",
          "traits": [
            {
